Grammar

    0 $accept: program $end

    1 program: stmt_list

    2 stmt_list: stmt_list statement
    3          | %empty

    4 statement: line_stmt
    5          | rect_stmt
    6          | circle_stmt
    7          | text_stmt

    8 line_stmt: LINE LPAREN number COMMA number COMMA number COMMA number RPAREN COLOR color_name WIDTH number SEMICOLON

    9 rect_stmt: RECT LPAREN number COMMA number COMMA number COMMA number RPAREN COLOR color_name WIDTH number rect_fill_part SEMICOLON

   10 rect_fill_part: FILL color_name
   11               | NOFILL

   12 circle_stmt: CIRCLE LPAREN number COMMA number COMMA number RPAREN COLOR color_name WIDTH number circle_fill_part SEMICOLON

   13 circle_fill_part: FILL color_name
   14                 | NOFILL

   15 text_stmt: TEXT LPAREN number COMMA number COMMA string RPAREN COLOR color_name SIZE number SEMICOLON

   16 number: NUMBER

   17 string: STRING

   18 color_name: IDENTIFIER


Terminals, with rules where they appear

    $end (0) 0
    error (256)
    LINE (258) 8
    RECT (259) 9
    CIRCLE (260) 12
    TEXT (261) 15
    LPAREN (262) 8 9 12 15
    RPAREN (263) 8 9 12 15
    COMMA (264) 8 9 12 15
    SEMICOLON (265) 8 9 12 15
    COLOR (266) 8 9 12 15
    WIDTH (267) 8 9 12
    FILL (268) 10 13
    NOFILL (269) 11 14
    SIZE (270) 15
    NUMBER (271) 16
    STRING (272) 17
    IDENTIFIER (273) 18


Nonterminals, with rules where they appear

    $accept (19)
        on left: 0
    program (20)
        on left: 1
        on right: 0
    stmt_list (21)
        on left: 2 3
        on right: 1 2
    statement (22)
        on left: 4 5 6 7
        on right: 2
    line_stmt (23)
        on left: 8
        on right: 4
    rect_stmt (24)
        on left: 9
        on right: 5
    rect_fill_part (25)
        on left: 10 11
        on right: 9
    circle_stmt (26)
        on left: 12
        on right: 6
    circle_fill_part (27)
        on left: 13 14
        on right: 12
    text_stmt (28)
        on left: 15
        on right: 7
    number (29)
        on left: 16
        on right: 8 9 12 15
    string (30)
        on left: 17
        on right: 15
    color_name (31)
        on left: 18
        on right: 8 9 10 12 13 15


State 0

    0 $accept: . program $end

    $end    reduce using rule 3 (stmt_list)
    LINE    reduce using rule 3 (stmt_list)
    RECT    reduce using rule 3 (stmt_list)
    CIRCLE  reduce using rule 3 (stmt_list)
    TEXT    reduce using rule 3 (stmt_list)

    program    go to state 1
    stmt_list  go to state 2


State 1

    0 $accept: program . $end

    $end  shift, and go to state 3


State 2

    1 program: stmt_list .
    2 stmt_list: stmt_list . statement

    LINE    shift, and go to state 4
    RECT    shift, and go to state 5
    CIRCLE  shift, and go to state 6
    TEXT    shift, and go to state 7

    $end  reduce using rule 1 (program)

    statement    go to state 8
    line_stmt    go to state 9
    rect_stmt    go to state 10
    circle_stmt  go to state 11
    text_stmt    go to state 12


State 3

    0 $accept: program $end .

    $default  accept


